      <lg xml:id="TolE0331">
<l>nāṭpeyark kiḷavi mēṟkiḷan taṉṉa</l>
<l>vattu māṉmicai varainilai yiṉṟē</l>
<l>yoṟṟumey keṭuta leṉmaṉār pulavar</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The sound <foreign xml:lang="ta">m</foreign> followed by the sound <foreign xml:lang="ta">v</foreign> is shortened.<note
              place="foot">i.e to quarter of a <foreign xml:lang="ta">mātrā,</foreign> e.g. in <foreign xml:lang="ta">nilam valitu.</foreign> Interpolation ? Cf. Comment.</note></l>
      </lg>
    </div>
